posting_body: ['Stevens Square Studio 1 block to  MCAD/Downtown, close to MCTC, UMN', 'Property Address', '1905 Stevens Ave. SO.', '| 206 | Minneapolis, MN 55403', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Gardner Investments, Inc. |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'We are offering at 1905 Stevens Ave So.', ' this one of a kind Studio apartment.', ' This  cozy apartment is around 366 square feet and come with a separate kitchen with built in benches and kitchen table, private bathroom with tub and shower, and closet.', '  The solid wood panels with built in mirrors is amazing.', 'We are located on many bus lines - one direct to the U of M, only 2 blocks from MCAD and a five minute walk to downtown.', ' We allow cats and dogs for additional rent and $200.00 non refundable pet deposit.', ' Off-street parking is available for an additional charge.', ' There is on line rent payment and maintenance requests.', 'For more information about our classic apartments and homes for rent or to apply on line go to <URL>', 'Units vary', 'This is a non-smoking building.', 'Amenities', 'hardwood floors', 'natural woodwork', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Recessed floor to ceiling mirrors', 'laundry on site', 'on-line rent payment', 'On direct bus line to West Bank', 'On site friendly & helpful management', 'on line rent payment', 'on site management', 'many shops and restaurants nearby', 'Walk to Downtown', '2 blocks from MCAD', 'MCTC', 'common area & parking lot camera surveilance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 366', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $760.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $760.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
